<template>
  <v-app>
    <v-container>
      <!-- Top Bar -->
      <v-app-bar app color="blue darken-2" dark>
        <!-- Burger menu icon -->
        <v-btn icon @click="drawer = !drawer">
          <v-icon>mdi-menu</v-icon>
        </v-btn>
        <!-- Title -->
        <v-toolbar-title>{{ userName }}</v-toolbar-title>
        <v-spacer></v-spacer>
        <!-- Logout button -->
        <v-btn icon @click="logout">
          <v-icon>mdi-logout</v-icon>
        </v-btn>
      </v-app-bar>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <v-navigation-drawer app v-model="drawer" color="blue darken-2" dark>
        <v-list dense>
          <v-list-item
            v-for="(item, index) in sidebarItems"
            :key="index"
            @click="navigate(index)"
          >
            <v-list-item-action>
              <v-icon>{{ item.icon }}</v-icon>
            </v-list-item-action>
            <v-list-item-content>
              <v-list-item-title>{{ item.title }}</v-list-item-title>
            </v-list-item-content>
          </v-list-item>
        </v-list>
      </v-navigation-drawer>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <v-main>
        <v-col cols="12" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto">
          <v-card class="mx-auto" max-width="800">
            <v-card-title class="blue darken-2 white--text">
              Upload PDF Files
            </v-card-title>
            <v-card-text>
              <v-row>
                <v-col
                  v-for="(fileInfo, fieldName) in pdfFiles"
                  :key="fieldName"
                  cols="12"
                  md="6"
                >
                  <v-card class="mb-3">
                    <v-card-title>{{ fieldName }}</v-card-title>
                    <v-file-input
                      v-model="pdfFiles[fieldName].file"
                      accept=".pdf"
                      :label="'Select ' + fieldName"
                    ></v-file-input>
                    <v-card-actions>
                      <v-btn
                        v-if="fileInfo.submitted"
                        color="green"
                        @click="downloadFile(fileInfo._id)"
                      >
                        Download
                      </v-btn>
                      <v-btn
                        v-if="fileInfo.submitted"
                        color="red"
                        @click="deleteFile(fileInfo._id, fieldName)"
                      >
                        Delete
                      </v-btn>
                    </v-card-actions>
                  </v-card>
                </v-col>
              </v-row>
            </v-card-text>
            <v-divider class="my-4"></v-divider>
            <v-card-actions>
              <v-btn color="blue darken-2" @click="submitForm">Submit</v-btn>
              <v-btn color="primary" @click="downloadAllFiles"
                >Download All Files</v-btn
              >
            </v-card-actions>
          </v-card>
        </v-col>
      </v-main>
    </v-container>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios'

export default {
  data () {
    return {
      userName: localStorage.getItem('userName'),
      pdfFiles: {
        'Solicitud de residencias profesionales': {
          _id: '',
          file: null,
          submitted: false
        },
        'Carta de presentaciÃ³n': {
          _id: '',
          file: null,
          submitted: false
        }
      },
      submittedFiles: {},
      drawer: false,
      sidebarItems: [
        { title: 'Proyecto', icon: 'mdi-folder-outline' },
        { title: 'Asesorias', icon: 'mdi-account-plus-outline' },
        { title: 'Archivos', icon: 'mdi-file-document-outline' }
      ],
      userId: localStorage.getItem('id')
    }
  },
  mounted () {
    this.fetchFileData()
  },
  methods: {
    async fetchFileData () {
      try {
        const response = await axios.get('http://localhost:3000/archivos')
        this.submittedFiles = response.data.reduce((acc, file) => {
          acc[file.filename] = {
            _id: file._id,
            submitted: true
          }
          return acc
        }, {})
        for (const key in this.pdfFiles) {
          if (this.submittedFiles[key]) {
            this.pdfFiles[key]._id = this.submittedFiles[key]._id
            this.pdfFiles[key].submitted = true
          }
        }
      } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error fetching files:', error)
      }
    },
    navigate (index) {
      switch (index) {
        case 0:
          this.$router.push('/student')
          break
        case 1:
          this.$router.push('/student/asesorias')
          break
        case 2:
          this.$router.push('/student/archivos')
          break
        default:
          break
      }
    },
    logout () {
      localStorage.removeItem('token')
      localStorage.removeItem('user')
      this.$router.push('/login')
    },
    async submitForm () {
      try {
        for (const [fieldName, fileInfo] of Object.entries(this.pdfFiles)) {
          if (fileInfo.file && !fileInfo.submitted) {
            const formData = new FormData()
            formData.append('file', fileInfo.file)
            const response = await axios.post('http://localhost:3000/upload-archivo', formData, {
              headers: {
                'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data'
              }
            })
            this.pdfFiles[fieldName]._id = response.data.file._id
            this.pdfFiles[fieldName].submitted = true
          }
        }
        this.fetchFileData() // Refresh the submitted files list
      } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error uploading files:', error)
      }
    },
    downloadAllFiles () {
      // Download all files logic
    },
    async downloadFile (fileId) {
      try {
        const response = await axios.get(`http://localhost:3000/archivos/${fileId}`, {
          responseType: 'blob'
        })
        const url = window.URL.createObjectURL(new Blob([response.data]))
        const link = document.createElement('a')
        link.href = url
        link.setAttribute('download', 'file.pdf') // Change the file name as needed
        document.body.appendChild(link)
        link.click()
      } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error downloading file:', error)
      }
    },
    async deleteFile (fileId, fieldName) {
      try {
        await axios.delete(`http://localhost:3000/archivos/${fileId}`)
        this.pdfFiles[fieldName]._id = ''
        this.pdfFiles[fieldName].file = null
        this.pdfFiles[fieldName].submitted = false
      } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error deleting file:', error)
      }
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
.v-btn i {
  color: white;
}
</style>
